sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant API as API Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Cache as Redis

    C->>GW: POST /api/v1/orders
    GW->>Auth: Validate JWT
    Auth-->>GW: 200 OK (user_id)
    GW->>API: Forward request

    API->>Cache: GET cache:user:{id}
    Cache-->>API: MISS
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?
    DB-->>API: User row
    API->>Cache: SET cache:user:{id} (TTL 300s)

    API->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO orders (...)
    API->>DB: UPDATE products SET stock = stock - 1
    DB-->>API: COMMIT OK

    API-->>GW: 201 Created {order_id}
    GW-->>C: 201 Created

    Note over API,Cache: 异步通知
    API-)MQ: publish order.created
